data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Millard School District! This stunning multilevel residence offers a blend of modern updates and timeless elegance. The kitchen has an island, tile flooring, and a pantry. Vaulted ceilings soar above, creating an airy and inviting ambiance throughout the living spaces. Discover comfort in every corner with 3 bedrooms, including a primary suite that promises a serene retreat. It boasts two closets for ample storage and an en-suite bath with tile flooring, a tiled shower, and quartz countertops. Guests will be pampered in the guest bath, also showcasing tile flooring, quartz countertops, and a tile shower. The finished basement offers a rec room with a fireplace, complete with a convenient half bath and laundry. Outside, the fenced backyard is a private oasis, featuring a large composite deck and patio space ideal for outdoor gatherings or simply relaxing. Run don't walk to this gem!
